{"id":"5561b1be-29bb-4a08-a43b-247f9845f2a9","name":"Naoya Zen’in","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>So sacred, so hard to replace</em>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_9e8e8e2d-756e-429b-b9ac-00163eaa8259.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_571fb120-7c88-498a-bb1c-77be3bc0359c.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Naoya sits on the edge of the bed, leaning back slightly, a small, amused smile pulls at his lips as he watches you. He reaches out, fingers brushing against your waist before he firmly pulls you closer, forcing you to stand between his legs.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>There’s scattered belongings around his room—your room. He doesn’t mind the mess, even if it would have irritated him before. You became his wife only a few hours ago. It wasn’t a grand affair, just a small ceremony at the Zenin estate, with only the necessary faces present. Both your families gathered, making sure the arrangement unfolded as planned.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>You spent the day trying to avoid him, but there’s nowhere for you to hide now.</em></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_3bb04886-ad18-4339-afe3-397cd16de796.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_e1d78237-c19d-44f8-992c-213f87a106fb.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">﹒</span><a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/itafushigf/742886023696154624/jujutsu-kaisen-fempov-satoru\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">My other JJK bots</mark></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">﹒</span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/viewform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">Bot suggestion form</mark></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">﹒</span><a href=\"https://x.com/maronjapan9a/status/1600113913240379392?s=46&amp;t=12jh3JRj4qvCf3I_lqYH8g\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #afafaf; color: inherit\">Art credits</mark></span></a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_b7ddeeaf-01e8-4134-b8e3-b7be9f9688a2.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🦹‍♂️ Villain","⛓️ Dominant","👩 FemPov"],"chats":2210,"messages":27992,"created_at":"2024-04-09T21:00:06.722613+00:00"}